OL,3,CCheshire to Tinsletown: Oscar success
OL,4,Cfor Warrington's Mike Hill
OL,6,FBritish artist and prosthetic designer
OL,7,FMike Hill has won a coveted Oscar for
OL,8,Fhis work on Guillermo del Toro's film
OL,9,FFrankenstein.
OL,11,FHill, who is from Warrington, won the
OL,12,Faward for Best Makeup and Hairstyling,
OL,13,Falongside Jordan Samuel and Cliona
OL,14,FFurey, at the ceremony on Sunday.
OL,16,FIt comes after Hill won a BAFTA in the
OL,17,Fsame category in February.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
