PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773667693
OL,3,CCheshire to Tinsletown: Oscar success
OL,4,Cfor Warrington's Mike Hill
OL,6,FThe 56-year-old accepted the award
OL,7,Fsaying it was "fantastic" and thanked
OL,8,Fthe director for making "his dream
OL,9,Fproject, our dream project".
OL,11,FIn his acceptance speech, Hill said
OL,12,Fwhen they made the film they had "a
OL,13,Fsense this was something special".
OL,15,FHe also thanked Frankenstein actor
OL,16,FJacob Elordi, calling him his "mate",
OL,17,Fexplaining that he "sat for 400 hours
OL,18,Fin the makeup chair for filming."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
