OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773667693
OL,3,CCheshire to Tinsletown: Oscar success
OL,4,Cfor Warrington's Mike Hill
OL,6,FOne of the big UK hopes for success
OL,7,Fwas in the category for best
OL,8,Fsupporting actress, where the nominees
OL,9,Fincluded Manchester's Wunmi Mosaku,
OL,10,Ffor her role in the horror film
OL,11,FSinners.
OL,13,FBut Mosaku ` who has joint British-
OL,14,FNigerian nationality and moved to
OL,15,FHulme as a baby ` lost out to the
OL,16,FAmerican Amy Madigan, who won for her
OL,17,Fpart in the supernatural mystery
OL,18,FWeapons.
